<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Document</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css\style.css">
		<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/e107b5abdd.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<section>
			<h1>Welcome to the Behavioural Questions RESTful API Guide</h1>
			<p>Records will be in JSON format:</p>
			<code
				>{</br> "_id": a unique ID Number, in BSON format allocated automatically.</br> "question": a String - "Question must be
				in the format - Can you give me an example of a time when X? Don't be
				tempted to lead",</br> "answer": a String - "Answer with CAR - Cause, Action,
				Result. Don't use hypotheticals, don't generalise - think of a specific
				example",</br> "answered": a boolean "TRUE",</br> "values": An array of strings with
				leadership values [], </br>}
			</code>
		</section>
        <nav>
            <a href="/"><li>Behavioural Questions RESTful API Guide</li></a>
            <a href="/list"><li>Generate a List of Behavioural Questions</li></a>
            <a href="/newQuestion"><li>Submit a new Question to the Database</li></a>
        </nav>
        <h1>Submit a New Question</h1>
        <h2>Complete the fields then click Submit </h2>
		<p>
			question and answer must be a string, answered is a boolean and values
			is a series of strings separated by commas
		</p>
		<form action="/submitQuestion">
			<input type="text" placeholder="question" name="question">
			<input type="text" placeholder="answer" name="answer">
			<input type="text" placeholder="answered" name="answered">
			<input type="text" placeholder="values" name="values">
			<input type="submit">
		</form>
		<h2>
			Question List
		</h2>
		<ul class="random">
			<% for (let i=0; i< info.length; i++) {%>
				<li class="random">
					<span><%= info[i].question%></span>
					<i class="fa-solid fa-recycle"></i>
					<i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i>

				</li>
			<% } %>
		</ul>
		<script src="js/main.js"></script>
    </body>